sets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620f96dfe657b893332fa09f61cec34acd303cf9","tid":379582,"uid":34891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十六湖同Dubrovnik必去，個人推介Split，不夜城，同埋可以搭船去Hvar同其他小島。<br />\n如果想睇海風琴都可以去埋Zadar。</blockquote><br />\n5日咋喎 應該玩唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五日玩十六湖+Split+Dubrovnik都勉強夠嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好喺Zagreb stay咁耐同喺Split出外島就得"},{"pid":"3ad03a6a252ecafeff19c2898dd98c41cce88f48","tid":379582,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十六湖同Dubrovnik必去，個人推介Split，不夜城，同埋可以搭船去Hvar同其他小島。<br />\n如果想睇海風琴都可以去埋Zadar。</blockquote><br />\n5日咋喎 應該玩唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五日玩十六湖+Split+Dubrovnik都勉強夠嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好喺Zagreb stay咁耐同喺Split出外島就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭去Dubrovnik 都用成日  除非坐飛機  不過而家都仲係好熱  去十六湖 zadar rovinj 差不多了   如果識揸車   揸車會好啲   因為point to point 巴士唔係好密"},{"pid":"db688e9d4854869477f294d99166cd8c090f45d5","tid":379582,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:53:35.000Z","msg":"我自己去過有印象既係Porec, Rijeka 好有印象，得五日唔好去十六湖，又遠又多人，唔會浪漫。<br />\n<br />\ndubrovnik超級遠，睇你有冇興趣去<br />\n但我覺得Zadar係應該要去。<br />\n有海琴風伴奏睇日落，勁浪漫。<br />\n本身個town係古城都好好行。"},{"pid":"761a921e6d50a0eb9762c2c62f9878292717b6d7","tid":379582,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T00:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十六湖同Dubrovnik必去，個人推介Split，不夜城，同埋可以搭船去Hvar同其他小島。<br />\n如果想睇海風琴都可以去埋Zadar。</blockquote><br />\n5日咋喎 應該玩唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五日玩十六湖+Split+Dubrovnik都勉強夠嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好喺Zagreb stay咁耐同喺Split出外島就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭去Dubrovnik 都用成日  除非坐飛機  不過而家都仲係好熱  去十六湖 zadar rovinj 差不多了   如果識揸車   揸車會好啲   因為point to point 巴士唔係好密</blockquote><br />\n我本身諗住住朝早九點個班巴士, 遲料少miss左就要等到下午五點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2bfaeaa4b922123fffab298a1f79102957214f","tid":379582,"uid":128101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T01:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同一個曖昧緊既女仔去🤗</blockquote><br />\n同佢全日留係酒店，完。"},{"pid":"eafe6d20ebc15558e8e712f082d9ee4dbd28f40b","tid":379582,"uid":75442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T01:10:46.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完<br />\n有車牌就租車<br />\nDubrovnik一日<br />\nSplit兩日<br />\n十六湖一日半<br />\n夠晒"},{"pid":"f7864b0feed903a98e5baac1981ba81d5ce6e251","tid":379582,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>十六湖同Dubrovnik必去，個人推介Split，不夜城，同埋可以搭船去Hvar同其他小島。<br />\n如果想睇海風琴都可以去埋Zadar。</blockquote><br />\n5日咋喎 應該玩唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五日玩十六湖+Split+Dubrovnik都勉強夠嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好喺Zagreb stay咁耐同喺Split出外島就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭去Dubrovnik 都用成日  除非坐飛機  不過而家都仲係好熱  去十六湖 zadar rovinj 差不多了   如果識揸車   揸車會好啲   因為point to point 巴士唔係好密</blockquote><br />\n我本身諗住住朝早九點個班巴士, 遲料少miss左就要等到下午五點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得克羅地亞下面靚係好靚  不過仲係好熱   日頭個太陽令你唔想出門口  上面就涼啲  你得五日  無謂哂時間落去"},{"pid":"8e7079af6a6cc278fe31b0c99f4166f02016027e","tid":379582,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"影風景既話Hvar+Blue Cave+其他島仔都好正<br />\n不過你得5日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bf80783e01600ec3a9d2f3de919c5a493478e8","tid":379582,"uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:53:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將會去克羅地亞5日 <br />\n小弟鐘意影下lanscape相 <br />\n有冇地方係必去?<br />\n(我知五日唔會夠玩不過無晒假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n五日包唔包飛機? <br />\n如果包埋得三日。<br />\n去十六湖算啦～<br />\n再唔係只去dubrovnik算。<br />\n去浪漫唔係去投胎嘛！"}]}